meanings: (어떤 장소로) come, (나타나다) turn up, show up, (방문하다) visit
Something that is supposed to come has come

meanings.meaning: motion to a person to come
shout to[for] a person to come
buzz for one’s secretary to come soon
beckon to a person to come nearer
